**Before executing:**
- [ ] Verify command correctness
- [ ] Check for destructive operations
- [ ] Confirm file paths
- [ ] Validate inputs

**During execution:**
- [ ] Monitor for errors
- [ ] Provide progress updates
- [ ] Handle failures gracefully
- [ ] Log important actions

